metadata.description: This DeArt is about autonomy, courage and freedom. It represents the total liberation of the DeArtists in relation to the centralized hypercapitalist technology companies. Now I have my own contract and my own NFT store. Perhaps this is the true representation of the totally decentralized art. Goodbye censorship! Goodbye intermediaries! Goodbye bosses! #DeArt #GlitchArt #NeoExpressionism #Collage #Liberation #Autonomy #Courage #Freedom #DIY #P2P
metadata.name: LIBERATION!
